<ue5><m2>It's clear that Miami's share of the pie is unlikely to increase (--) even with more service. Some say the real impact of new gateways will be felt if American Airlines offers so much service in Miami that other airlines seeking niches locate elsewhere.<ql>
<m1><ql>
<ql>
<ql>
